{"tid":307187,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官宣！英超中遊隊簽下J洛！","createTime":"2017-07-03T07:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T07:12:11.000Z","uid":2500,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af45df83a890bcfd1fb9a6cce5930f0cb3498595","tid":307187,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:16:05.000Z","msg":"　　<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/151447_e511aa8dab9d1af4c8eb625be4a4cab5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F151447_e511aa8dab9d1af4c8eb625be4a4cab5.jpg&h=31df4eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英超西布朗隊正式從修咸頓簽下了前鋒傑伊-洛迪古斯，轉會費為1200萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n　　今年27歲的洛迪古斯和西布朗簽下了一份為期五年的合約，他成為了西布朗歷史上身價並列第二貴的收購。<br />\n<br />\n　　2012年，洛迪古斯從般尼加盟修咸頓，當時的轉會費是600萬英鎊。在修咸頓效力的五年時間里，洛迪古斯飽受傷病困擾，總共只攻入過35個入球。2014年他曾因為膝蓋韌帶重傷而傷停了一年多，上季也只在英超正選出場過9次。在國際足球舞台，他曾有過一次英格蘭隊出場。<br />\n<br />\n　　談到此次轉會，洛迪古斯說：「對於任何球員來說，最重要的事情是被人需要，普利斯（主教練）和西布朗明確告訴我，他們多麼想要我加盟。我很高興能加盟西布朗這樣的球隊，球隊里有很多頂級球員。」<br />\n<br />\n　　洛迪古斯上季英超數據：24場、9次正選、共出場881分鐘、5個入球、2次助攻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/7635231/6/20170703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F7635231%2F6%2F20170703&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=74c0145d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/7635231/6/20170703</a>"},{"pid":"b8d5a003b4f392cb7dc1eb599043bfea673eaafc","tid":307187,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"51fae8c32df1dadbef59264370350aac469abb84","tid":307187,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n我唔屌你個肉酸老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270d3e33dd617adbfc7edc9365cc4a0058ccbe83","tid":307187,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":